    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You place this shroud on a target creature, causing a small cloud to follow it and periodically strike it with lightning. Every time the target attempts to take a standard or full-round action, it takes electricity damage equal to 1d6 + your caster level (Reflex negates). This counts as taking place during the casting of a spell or the use of a sphere ability for the purpose of concentration checks. Each time the target fails a Reflex save against this shroud&#8217;s effects they must succeed at a Fortitude save or be deafened for one round.</p>\n",
